  <p class="gd-lede">Iceland's heliski season is, from start to finish, a spring season, and understanding what spring means on the Arctic coast is the key to planning a great trip. Here is what to expect from the weather, daylight and snow across March to mid-June, before you explore <a href="/packages">the packages</a> and <a href="/iceland">Iceland</a>.</p>
